

{"id":5387,"date":"2023-08-23T15:11:16","date_gmt":"2023-08-23T08:11:16","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tnt.locdt.site\/staging\/?p=5387"},"modified":"2023-08-29T16:48:33","modified_gmt":"2023-08-29T09:48:33","slug":"thu-thach-30-ngay-tap-luyen-de-co-than-hinh-can-doi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/thu-thach-30-ngay-tap-luyen-de-co-than-hinh-can-doi\/","title":{"rendered":"Th\u1eed th\u00e1ch 30 ng\u00e0y t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><em><strong>Th\u1eed th\u00e1ch 30 ng\u00e0y t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i: B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean thon g\u1ecdn trong 30 ng\u00e0y? B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n trong 30 ng\u00e0y? L\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n trong 30 ng\u00e0y?<\/strong><\/em><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u00dd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 trong 30 ng\u00e0y nghe c\u00f3 v\u1ebb qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. Xem h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a The New Gym v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c th\u1eed th\u00e1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n trong 30 ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #009fc2; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean thon g\u1ecdn trong 30 ng\u00e0y?<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4906\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4906\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4906 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/ha-nhiet-co-the.png\" alt=\"th\u1eed th\u00e1ch 30 ng\u00e0y, t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/ha-nhiet-co-the.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/ha-nhiet-co-the-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/ha-nhiet-co-the-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/ha-nhiet-co-the-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/ha-nhiet-co-the-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4906\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean thon g\u1ecdn trong 30 ng\u00e0y?<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 trong 30 ph\u00fat, trong khi \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 100kg. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 The New Gym bi\u1ebft ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong 30 ng\u00e0y &#8211; cho d\u00f9 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ea1y xa h\u01a1n, n\u00e2ng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i h\u01a1n v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp v\u1edbi d\u00e1ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n ho\u1eb7c nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. 30 ng\u00e0y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng nh\u1eefng th\u00f3i quen t\u1ed1t cho s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u00f3i quen l\u00e2u d\u00e0i gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi t\u1eeb trong ra ngo\u00e0i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi bi\u1ebfn n\u00f3 th\u00e0nh th\u1ee9 b\u1ea1n th\u00edch, th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi n\u00f3 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t sau 30 ng\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu ch\u1ea1y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n th\u00edch, t\u1ea1i sao kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch khi ch\u1ea1y? B\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch n\u00e0o b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eb7t ra, h\u00e3y bi\u1ebfn n\u00f3 th\u00e0nh th\u1eed th\u00e1ch khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #009fc2; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n trong 30 ng\u00e0y?<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4787\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4787\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4787 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-cam-thay-nham-chan-voi-viec-tap-luyen-cua-minh.png\" alt=\"th\u1eed th\u00e1ch 30 ng\u00e0y, t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-cam-thay-nham-chan-voi-viec-tap-luyen-cua-minh.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-cam-thay-nham-chan-voi-viec-tap-luyen-cua-minh-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-cam-thay-nham-chan-voi-viec-tap-luyen-cua-minh-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-cam-thay-nham-chan-voi-viec-tap-luyen-cua-minh-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-cam-thay-nham-chan-voi-viec-tap-luyen-cua-minh-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4787\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n trong 30 ng\u00e0y?<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Khi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i trong 30 ng\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. C\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nhanh h\u01a1n b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 n\u00f3 l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh, l\u00e2u d\u00e0i ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao ch\u00fang ta th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0103n ki\u00eang \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh t\u0103ng c\u00e2n sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. N\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u00e0 gi\u1eef d\u00e1ng, The New Gym khuy\u00ean b\u1ea1n n\u00ean t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c th\u00f3i quen t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh trong 30 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi n\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i. Sau 30 ng\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mong \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 s\u0103n ch\u1eafc, kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn xa h\u01a1n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><em>H\u00e3y nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nhanh h\u01a1n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng. T\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng th\u00f3i quen t\u1ed1t s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.<\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #009fc2; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>L\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n trong 30 ng\u00e0y?<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>1. X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4789\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4789\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4789 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-khong-biet-bat-dau-tu-dau.png\" alt=\"th\u1eed th\u00e1ch 30 ng\u00e0y, t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-khong-biet-bat-dau-tu-dau.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-khong-biet-bat-dau-tu-dau-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-khong-biet-bat-dau-tu-dau-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-khong-biet-bat-dau-tu-dau-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-khong-biet-bat-dau-tu-dau-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4789\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n trong 30 ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi l\u00e0 g\u00ec? B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 50 l\u1ea7n g\u1eadp b\u1ee5ng kh\u00f4ng? Ch\u1ea1y 30 ph\u00fat? Gi\u1eef Plank trong 2 ph\u00fat? N\u00e2ng t\u1ea1 40kg? \u0110\u1ec3 l\u1eadp k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cho h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n trong 30 ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean c\u00f3 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o m\u00e0 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o th\u00f3i quen c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>2. L\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cho nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4075\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4075\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4075 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/lich-trinh-tap-luyen.png\" alt=\"th\u1eed th\u00e1ch 30 ng\u00e0y, t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/lich-trinh-tap-luyen.png 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/lich-trinh-tap-luyen-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/lich-trinh-tap-luyen-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/lich-trinh-tap-luyen-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/lich-trinh-tap-luyen-1536x780.png 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/lich-trinh-tap-luyen-2048x1040.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4075\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">L\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cho nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eddi gian b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n b\u1ed5 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 trong 30 ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">V\u00ed d\u1ee5, b\u1ea1n r\u1ea3nh v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 Hai, th\u1ee9 T\u01b0 v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t cho m\u00ecnh th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp. B\u1ea1n th\u00edch t\u1eadp t\u1ea1 v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia l\u1ecbch t\u1eadp h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh 3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp to\u00e0n th\u00e2n, cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n nh\u1eafm m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00e0o c\u00e1c nh\u00f3m c\u01a1 3 l\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c l\u1ea7n, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00edch v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n kh\u1ecfe h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c t\u1ea1 nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 t\u0103ng d\u1ea7n trong nhi\u1ec1u bu\u1ed5i ho\u1eb7c nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian h\u01a1n khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1ecfe. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ho\u00e0n ch\u1ec9nh s\u1ebd cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i ph\u00eda sau.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>3. Xem x\u00e9t nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng kh\u00e1c m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4832\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4832\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4832 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/dung-bo-bua.png\" alt=\"th\u1eed th\u00e1ch 30 ng\u00e0y, t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/dung-bo-bua.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/dung-bo-bua-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/dung-bo-bua-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/dung-bo-bua-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/dung-bo-bua-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4832\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Xem x\u00e9t nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng kh\u00e1c m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. \u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng s\u1ebd xem x\u00e9t c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kh\u00e1c trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea1n ng\u1ee7 c\u00f3 ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ea5c hay kh\u00f4ng. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n \u0111ang cung c\u1ea5p cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 t\u1eeb th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i nhi\u1ec1u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>4. \u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_5562\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5562\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5562 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Dam-bao-thoi-gian-nghi-ngoi-va-phuc-hoi-2.png\" alt=\"th\u1eed th\u00e1ch 30 ng\u00e0y, t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Dam-bao-thoi-gian-nghi-ngoi-va-phuc-hoi-2.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Dam-bao-thoi-gian-nghi-ngoi-va-phuc-hoi-2-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Dam-bao-thoi-gian-nghi-ngoi-va-phuc-hoi-2-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Dam-bao-thoi-gian-nghi-ngoi-va-phuc-hoi-2-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Dam-bao-thoi-gian-nghi-ngoi-va-phuc-hoi-2-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-5562\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n \u0111ang cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. Ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n n\u00e0o, v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap c\u01a1 b\u1eafp c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp ti\u1ebfp theo. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c 30 ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i H\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c (OTS), \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi l\u00e0m t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n trong 30 ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>5. Nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 th\u1ec3<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_5556\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5556\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5556 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Nhan-thuc-duoc-nhung-han-che-cua-co-the.png\" alt=\"th\u1eed th\u00e1ch 30 ng\u00e0y, t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Nhan-thuc-duoc-nhung-han-che-cua-co-the.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Nhan-thuc-duoc-nhung-han-che-cua-co-the-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Nhan-thuc-duoc-nhung-han-che-cua-co-the-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Nhan-thuc-duoc-nhung-han-che-cua-co-the-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Nhan-thuc-duoc-nhung-han-che-cua-co-the-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-5556\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 th\u1ec3<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">L\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c theo t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n d\u1ea7n d\u1ea7n. M\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn t\u1ed1t l\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 30 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 n\u00e0y, b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00e1c nh\u00f3m c\u01a1 ch\u00ednh. Ngo\u00e0i ra, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u1ec9 trong 30 ng\u00e0y th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u00eam v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng cu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u1eed th\u00e1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n trong 30 ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng th\u00eam \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c cho b\u1ea1n. Bi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n y\u00eau th\u00edch c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1eddi gian t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3,\u00a0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5<em> <a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/5-ly-do-nen-tap-luyen-cung-huan-luyen-vien-ca-nhan\/\">hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n<\/a><\/em> t\u1ea1i The New Gym c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1eb7t l\u1ecbch v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 PT s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n h\u00f3a d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean h\u1ec7:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/@thenewgymvn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Youtube The New Gym<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/thenewgymvietnam\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Fanpage The New Gym<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Hotline: 1900636920<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Th\u1eed th\u00e1ch 30 ng\u00e0y t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i: B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean thon g\u1ecdn trong 30 ng\u00e0y? B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n trong 30 ng\u